; mml2vgm Browser IDE - Drum Pattern Sample
; Demonstrates SSG drum patterns

@OPNA

; Part 0: Kick and Snare
@0 v100 l16 o5
  bd4 sn4 bd4 sn4 bd4 bd4 sn8 bd4 sn4 bd4 sn4 bd4 bd4 sn8

; Part 1: Hi-hats
@1 v80 l16 o6
  hh4 hh4 hh4 hh4 hh4 hh4 hh4 hh4

; Part 2: Toms
@2 v90 l8 o4
  tom4 tom4 tom8 tom4 tom4 tom8
